<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٧٢٨٢ - عَنْ مَعْمَرٍ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ قَتَادَةَ قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«لَا يُسْتَحْلَفُ أَحَدٌ بِالْمُصْحَفِ»</span>،<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٧٢٨٣ -<span class="c5"> قَالَ عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ:</span> <span class="c1">" وَكَانَ مَعْمَرٌ: يَكْرَهُ أَنْ يُسْتَحْلَفَ أَحَدٌ بِالْمُصْحَفِ "</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>